### unsetFlagsWhichSetDuringLiveAnalysis() {#ac1174d0ac0a156a3107668426402df15}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>void llvm::dwarf&#95;linker::parallel::CompileUnit::DIEInfo::unsetFlagsWhichSetDuringLiveAnalysis ()</>}
  labels = {["inline"]}>
<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> is a part of the linked output.

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> has children which are part of the linked output. <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> has children which are part of the type table. <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> is in module scope. <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> is in function scope. <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> is in anonymous namespace scope. <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> is available for ODR type deduplication. Track liveness for the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a>. Track liveness for the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a>.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/dwarflinker/lib/dwarflinker/parallel/dwarflinkercompileunit-h/#l00250">250</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/dwarflinker/lib/dwarflinker/parallel/dwarflinkercompileunit-h">DWARFLinkerCompileUnit.h</a>.
